			"updated": 1778898175260,
			"locked": false,
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"text": "Keys are kept in sorted order at all times.\n• left subtree  <  node key  <  right subtree  (BST rule)\n• An in-order walk (left → node → right) visits keys from smallest to largest.",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Keys are kept in sorted order at all times.\n• left subtree  <  node key  <  right subtree  (BST rule)\n• An in-order walk (left → node → right) visits keys from smallest to largest.",
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"baseline": 15,
			"index": "b0U",
			"autoResize": true,
			"rawText": "Keys are kept in sorted order at all times.\n• left subtree  <  node key  <  right subtree  (BST rule)\n• An in-order walk (left → node → right) visits keys from smallest to largest.",
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"link": null
		},
