			"fontSize": 19.5137815607054,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"text": "1) Search as if the key were already there — fall off at an empty child link.\n2) Attach new leaf with the key.\n3) Rebalance / recolor (red–black rotations, AVL fixes, …) so height stays O(log N).",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "1) Search as if the key were already there — fall off at an empty child link.\n2) Attach new leaf with the key.\n3) Rebalance / recolor (red–black rotations, AVL fixes, …) so height stays O(log N).",
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"baseline": 15,
			"index": "b10",
			"autoResize": true,
			"rawText": "1) Search as if the key were already there — fall off at an empty child link.\n2) Attach new leaf with the key.\n3) Rebalance / recolor (red–black rotations, AVL fixes, …) so height stays O(log N).",
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
