			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1778898175260,
			"locked": false,
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"text": "• Minimum: repeatedly take left child from root — O(log N) (or store pointer to leftmost).\n• Maximum: symmetric, go right.\n• Top‑K smallest (total keys = N): walk in-order from the minimum — stop after emitting K keys — typically\nO(K + log N) (reach far-left in O(log N), then K in-order steps).",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "• Minimum: repeatedly take left child from root — O(log N) (or store pointer to leftmost).\n• Maximum: symmetric, go right.\n• Top‑K smallest (total keys = N): walk in-order from the minimum — stop after emitting K keys — typically\nO(K + log N) (reach far-left in O(log N), then K in-order steps).",
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"baseline": 15,
			"index": "b14",
			"autoResize": true,
			"rawText": "• Minimum: repeatedly take left child from root — O(log N) (or store pointer to leftmost).\n• Maximum: symmetric, go right.\n• Top‑K smallest (total keys = N): walk in-order from the minimum — stop after emitting K keys — typically\nO(K + log N) (reach far-left in O(log N), then K in-order steps).",
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"link": null
		},
