			"updated": 1778898175260,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"text": "• Skip list (Redis sorted sets): probabilistic levels — expected O(log N) operations; different but similar use cases.\n• Sorted array + binary search: O(log N) lookup, O(N) insert — fine for read-mostly data.\n• B-trees / B+ trees: great on disk — used in databases and file indexes.",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "• Skip list (Redis sorted sets): probabilistic levels — expected O(log N) operations; different but similar use cases.\n• Sorted array + binary search: O(log N) lookup, O(N) insert — fine for read-mostly data.\n• B-trees / B+ trees: great on disk — used in databases and file indexes.",
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"baseline": 15,
			"index": "b17",
			"autoResize": true,
			"rawText": "• Skip list (Redis sorted sets): probabilistic levels — expected O(log N) operations; different but similar use cases.\n• Sorted array + binary search: O(log N) lookup, O(N) insert — fine for read-mostly data.\n• B-trees / B+ trees: great on disk — used in databases and file indexes.",
			"hasTextLink": false
		}
